messages.message: Private 2: Let's just get outta here!{N}Captain: Can't let them seize this MRV!
Captain: AWWW HOT HOT HOT!!!{N}Captain: That piece of crap!{N}Private 2: What now, captain!?{N}Private 1: It needs repairs, sir!{N}Captain: We'll kill 'em first!
Captain: Keep attacking anyway!{N}Private 1: Yes, sir!
Private 1: I can't control it!{N}Captain: What!?
